	smells like?[BR]
	[Pause 10]Probably like blood,[Pause 5] and other[BR]
	bad things.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I called a therapist and he said[BR]
	there was something seriously[BR]
	wrong with me.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	And yeah, that's fair.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I'm a bit of a [SizeWave]wacky[/fx] dude.[Wait][End]
}

#message:07:048
{
	[Style Right]
	I'm trying to get a meeting with[BR]
	my therapist, but get this![BR]
	[Pause 10]There's a big line just to get[BR]
	ahold of one.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Boy, if I'd known therapists were[BR]
	this busy, I would have kept[BR]
	smelling death.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I don't endorse it by the way.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Stay safe, kids.[Wait][End]
}

