	Chap, there's been a new spill[BR]
	o' the tea on this bleeding red[BR]
	isle to the south, dare.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Wave]Ho ho ho![/fx][Pause 5][BR]
	The isle ain't the important part,[BR]
	mate.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
